30
00:02:26,338 --> 00:02:30,386
You know the live channel that talks about the weather all day?

31
00:02:30,386 --> 00:02:35,356
Does anyone else out there watch it all day besides me?

32
00:02:37,179 --> 00:02:41,894
Next up, let's take a look at tomorrow's weather.

33
00:02:43,122 --> 00:02:46,424
Here's what's on the radar.

34
00:02:49,829 --> 00:02:53,063
It'll stop raining in many areas,

35
00:02:53,063 --> 00:02:57,234
